      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata N 1006 </s>
            </p>
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> La gelosia 
                   Jalouise</s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>La gelosia</head>
               <figDesc> Due bambini a teatro, lei guarda lui con aria gelosa, data dal fatto che lui stia guardando le ballerine con il binocolo
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Modena lì 30/5 - 1917</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Oliva mia, <lb/>            domani ti parlerò di tante cose <lb/>            buone e belle che ti fanno pia - <lb/>            cere, ti parlerò dei miei studi <lb/>            della mia vita, dell'animo mio <lb/>            oggi no è la vigilia è il <lb/>            giorno che precorre il <gap reason="illegible"/>
                     <lb/>            delle pasfioni, della fede, della <lb/>            volontà. <lb/>            Domani ti voglio spedire qual - <lb/>            che cosa che ti ricordi quel giorno, <lb/>            qualche cosa di indelebile che nell'av - <lb/>            venire ricordandoti di quello, tu posfa <lb/>            ripensare al giorno in cui ti fu dona - <lb/>            to, al giorno in cui il tuo Giovannino <lb/>            ha voluto amarti. <lb/>            Un bacio </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 214 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
